{"tid":1446644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登民意統計","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:03:19.000Z","uid":40318,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33c481333ba3c30e1c55aee7f28d61cebe310f92","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"經過今日睇到狗可以用盡下三濫陰招去打手足 大家係咪要考慮吓要變吓策略 由明刀明鎗上街發夢到日常生活放暗箭<br />\n<br />\n以下開放統計投票<br />\n<br />\n依個post純粹統計民意 並非鼓吹犯法<br />\n我反對一切違法行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e767210362d0166cee342a611bdade2cd6efa0e3","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9522eb7d1d846ab5ef67ca87e5d4b02babc75b0","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8804d0c954d2c02b67f4905e7c15b80038a88a46","tid":1446644,"uid":35233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:39.000Z","msg":"唔係真勇武既唔好亂咁投啦拜託"},{"pid":"7a0d1df693d0c678ec84228a7879dbdab4a2804a","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e8879630b4a6e8a11fc7e1f2e2daf53b4e8334","tid":1446644,"uid":108225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"好希望大家可以諗一諗<br />\n有一個比較好嘅共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家政府話大家好暴力 要全港市民做對立<br />\n大家可唔可以忍受一星期 停一停 做文宣<br />\n<br />\n之後做一個超大型嘅遊行集會 但唔好戀戰<br />\n真係和理非非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢段時間set死線<br />\n 同全香港市民講暴力係因為政府漠視民意<br />\n<br />\n如果過咗死線之後都係冇回應嘅話 先再捲土重來<br />\n將個責任放返落政府度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣只係挨打 場運動都會越嚟越散<br />\n不分化 匆忘初心"},{"pid":"2b70a4b84b682f4159b76628ab9914d76daa213c","tid":1446644,"uid":279650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"做咩都不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要說推，請說<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n<br />\n文宣/民間記者會！！！！"},{"pid":"0ec51c97e1db58e8628a0dddbc8efac0b464f3a3","tid":1446644,"uid":265273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請立即發動第二次大罷工大罷市！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a8ccf04cb9ffa7031c681e73eec4329c40586d99","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申：反對一切暴力且違法行為<br />\n此post只係民意統計"},{"pid":"69a85cc0141b03639ec3f73c9b7685be75adf194","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正負評投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c4392d826da33d71af21865a8bb3d8df61482e25","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申：反對一切暴力且違法行為<br />\n此post只係民意統計"},{"pid":"e10cdb18749f6bb26ec45c6b2d7e94e698c9ba91","tid":1446644,"uid":40318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申：反對一切